Outbreak statistics [rates apparent, expressed as percentages]:
Species / Morbidity rate / Mortality rate / Case fatality rate / Proportion susceptible animals lost*
Goats / ** / ** / 97.32 / **
Sheep / **/ **/ 78 /**
Sheep/goats / **/ **/ ** /**
*Removed from the susceptible population through death, destruction and/or slaughter
**Not calculated because of missing information

Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: Illegal movement of animals

Control measures
Measures applied: screening; no vaccination; no treatment of affected animals
Measures to be applied: stamping out; vaccination in response to the outbreak(s)

Diagnostic test results
Laboratory name and type / Species / Test / Test date / Result
African Union Pan African Veterinary Vaccine Center (AU-PANVAC), Ethiopia (Regional Reference Laboratory) / Sheep/goats / competitive ELISA (c-ELISA) / 10 Jul 2015 / Positive

Future reporting
The event is continuing. Weekly follow-up reports will be submitted.

[The location of the outbreaks can be seen on the interactive map included in the OIE report at the source URL above.]

